Task 1:
	we need To implement the average Example for students With while Loop and For loop:

	        int grade;
            int sum=0;
            for (int i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
               System.out.println(" Enter your grad :");
               grade=scanner.nextInt();
               sum+=grade;
            }
            System.out.println(" The summation of all grades is :"+ sum);

            //==============================================
            int studentGrade;
            int allGrades=0;
            int counter=0;
            while(counter<=4){
                System.out.println(" Enter your grad :");
                studentGrade=scanner.nextInt();
                allGrades+=studentGrade;
                counter++;
            }
            System.out.println(" The summation of all grades is :"+ allGrades);

