Task 3:
Write a program that prints out even numbers from  2 to 20 .
hint You would need to increase the counter with 2
Enhance your code to bring the summation of even numbers and odd numbers from 2 to 20

   int EvenSum=0;
        int OddSum=0;
        for (int i = 2; i < 20; i++) {
          if(i % 2 == 0){
              System.out.println("this value is even : "+ i);
              EvenSum+=i;
              System.out.println("----------------------------------");
          }else{
              System.out.println("this value is odd : "+ i);
              OddSum+=i;
          }
        }
        System.out.println("The summation of even number is :"+EvenSum);
        System.out.println("The summation of odd number is :"+OddSum);

